msgid "Tassā evamassa: "
msgstr "She might think, "

msgctxt "an9.35:3.3"
msgid "‘yannūnāhaṃ agatapubbañceva disaṃ gaccheyyaṃ, akhāditapubbāni ca tiṇāni khādeyyaṃ, apītapubbāni ca pānīyāni piveyyan’ti. "
msgstr "‘Why don’t I go somewhere I’ve never been before? I could eat grass and drink water that I’ve never tried before.’ "

